item.title: CVE-2021-41561|2024-08-04T03:15:29.260Z -- apache%20software%20foundation -- apache%20parquet
item.description: Improper Input Validation vulnerability in Parquet-MR of Apache Parquet allows an attacker to DoS by malicious Parquet files. This issue affects Apache Parquet-MR version 1.9.0 and later versions.
